<div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6 space-y-8">
    <div class="flex items-start justify-between gap-4">
        <div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900">资产负债率知识库</h2>
            <p class="mt-2 text-gray-600 text-sm">资产负债率是“杠杆/风险承受力”的快速刻度。它不直接等于风险大小，但能帮助你判断公司在利率、景气和现金流压力下的抗压能力。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-sm">
            <a href="/kb" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">知识库</a>
            <span class="text-gray-300 mx-2">/</span>
            <a href="/" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">股票列表</a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <section class="space-y-3">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800">1. 资产负债率是什么？</h3>
        <div class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed space-y-2">
            <p>资产负债率 = 总负债 / 总资产。</p>
            <p>直观含义：资产里有多少比例是通过负债融资形成的。数值越高，杠杆越大，偿付压力越高；数值越低，财务结构越稳健。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-4 text-gray-700 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            <div class="font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-1">三个关键点</div>
            <div>同一个数字，在不同行业含义差异极大。</div>
            <div>要区分“经营性负债”与“有息负债”。</div>
            <div>要结合现金流与利息覆盖能力，而不是只看一个比例。</div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="space-y-3">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800">2. 行业差异：为什么银行/地产看起来都很高？</h3>
        <div class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed space-y-2 text-sm">
            <div><span class="font-semibold text-gray-800">金融（银行/保险）</span>：负债主要是存款/保费准备金，属于业务模式的一部分，资产负债率天然高，需要用资本充足率、资产质量、净息差等指标配合。</div>
            <div><span class="font-semibold text-gray-800">地产</span>：高度依赖融资与周转，资产负债率往往偏高，需重点看现金流、短债压力、预收款结构、去化与政策周期。</div>
            <div><span class="font-semibold text-gray-800">制造/消费</span>：一般更适合用资产负债率做横向比较，配合 ROE 与经营现金流可快速判断“盈利质量 + 杠杆风险”。</div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="space-y-3">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800">3. 经营性负债 vs 有息负债</h3>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
            <div class="bg-green-50 border border-green-100 rounded-lg p-4 text-green-900/90 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                <div class="font-semibold text-green-900 mb-1">经营性负债（相对“友好”）</div>
                <div>应付账款、预收款、合同负债等，更多是经营周转形成，通常成本更低，但也反映对供应链/客户的议价关系。</div>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-yellow-50 border border-yellow-100 rounded-lg p-4 text-yellow-900/90 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                <div class="font-semibold text-yellow-900 mb-1">有息负债（更关注“压力”）</div>
                <div>短期借款、长期借款、公司债等，需要付利息并到期偿还。利率上行或景气下行时更容易放大风险。</div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed text-sm">
            <div class="font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-1">实用结论</div>
            <div>资产负债率高不一定坏，但如果有息负债占比也高、且经营现金流不稳，则风险显著上升。</div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="space-y-3">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800">4. 常见误区</h3>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
            <div class="bg-yellow-50 border border-yellow-100 rounded-lg p-4 text-yellow-900/90 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                <div class="font-semibold text-yellow-900 mb-1">只看比例不看结构</div>
                <div>同样 60% 的资产负债率，可能是“应付账款为主”也可能是“短债为主”，风险完全不同。</div>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-yellow-50 border border-yellow-100 rounded-lg p-4 text-yellow-900/90 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                <div class="font-semibold text-yellow-900 mb-1">忽略现金流</div>
                <div>负债压力的本质是“现金流承受力”。经营现金流持续为正，杠杆更可控。</div>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-yellow-50 border border-yellow-100 rounded-lg p-4 text-yellow-900/90 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                <div class="font-semibold text-yellow-900 mb-1">周期行业的错觉</div>
                <div>景气上行时资产负债率看起来“没问题”，下行时利润与现金流收缩，杠杆风险会快速暴露。</div>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-yellow-50 border border-yellow-100 rounded-lg p-4 text-yellow-900/90 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                <div class="font-semibold text-yellow-900 mb-1">忽略表外与担保</div>
                <div>部分行业存在表外负担或担保链条，仅看报表口径可能低估风险。</div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="space-y-3">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800">5. 本系统里的负债口径</h3>
        <div class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed space-y-2 text-sm">
            <div><span class="font-semibold text-gray-800">资产负债率</span>：总负债 / 总资产 × 100%。</div>
            <div><span class="font-semibold text-gray-800">有息负债率</span>：数据源提供的有息负债占比（用于快速识别“负债结构偏融资型”）。</div>
            <div>两者都来自最新一期财报快照，因此建议结合财报期与行业特性解读。</div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="text-xs text-gray-500 leading-relaxed border-t border-gray-100 pt-4">
        <div>提示：以上内容仅用于解释指标与方法论，不构成任何投资建议。市场有风险，决策需自担。</div>
    </section>
</div>
